title: Breathing Fire (1991)
description:
Here is a curious low budget project featuring Jonathan Quan (Indiana Jones & Goonies) and Bolo Yeung (Bloodsport). Jerry Trimble, a world class kick boxer is also featured in this film. Laura Hamilton, the attractive blonde actress in this film, did one additional project then dropped out of public view. I picked up this gem at a video liquidator for 50 cents.

Trivia: The working title for this film was "Kung Fu Cubs".

XviD Avi
